which will be compared to the effective haircut of the transaction, ie B −1.</data>
      <data key="d4">Preamble</data>
    </node>
    <node id="OBL-0150">
      <data key="d2">obligation</data>
      <data key="d3">For a netting of SFTs an effective “portfolio” floor of the transaction must be computed as:
 ∑E   ∑C 
f = s s   t t −1
